text: WJCK may refer to: *WJCK (FM), a radio station (88.3 FM) in Anniston, Alabama, United States *WJCK-FM, former callsign of WLQI, a radio station (97.7 FM) in Rensselaer, Indiana, United States *WJCK-TV, former callsign of WWTI, a television station (TV 50) in Watertown, New York, United States
title: WJCK
